      <SupplementalInformationDetail>
        <FormAndLineReferenceDesc>Form 990-EZ, Part V, Line 34</FormAndLineReferenceDesc>
        <ExplanationTxt>Since the last filing, all three officers were replaced. Jodi Newell left the organization early in the year and was replaced with Kristen Peluso as President. John Shen stepped down as Secretary mid-year and was temporarily replaced with another officer before Brie d'Ayr joined the board as a permanent replacement more recently. Samuel Fieldman, who has been a long-term contractor with the organization, took over the role of Treasurer from Michael Monetta in December of 2021. He will remain in the role only until a more permanent treasurer can be found. The compensation listed for Mr. Fieldman is his regular contract amount. That amount did not change when he became Treasurer and he receives no additional money for that role.</ExplanationTxt>
